{"tid":874073,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"關於whatsapp backup","createTime":"2018-10-24T02:11:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T03:16:03.000Z","uid":107768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c1b12646d14354ed17ccda570458f0259290cc32","tid":874073,"uid":107768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T02:11:48.000Z","msg":"話說我whatsapp有個對話嘅Media全部無過落以家用緊部電話到，淨係得文字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我新機已經開始用緊，唔知點樣先可以將啲媒體過埋去新機到，又唔會搞到無左啲對話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問過Apple啲人話無得merge埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n於是send左email俾whatsapp又答答下又無答我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/24/101115_d790733487a69cd13c0b8c04f5f6c19d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F24%2F101115_d790733487a69cd13c0b8c04f5f6c19d.png&h=978b364e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係以家部電話嘅whatsapp，我舊機個啲仲係到㗎，但唔知點樣link返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/24/101135_e1e28ee19de68a29ccd4d9f6d36f1525.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F24%2F101135_e1e28ee19de68a29ccd4d9f6d36f1525.png&h=9f9492bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係whatsapp嘅回覆，我唔係好明。如果我restore左舊機嘅backup，咁我以家用個部電話開始嘅對話會唔會無左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望有好心人可以解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞左好耐都唔知點好，時不時攞返舊電話出黎睇，又驚一日壞機以後都無得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d92f56a87b99fdef5e6b272ee012f23a5815a0a3","tid":874073,"uid":9726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T03:16:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}